url: "https://github.com/muxueqingze/xuxiang-thinkflow"
abstract: "续想（ThinkFlow） is an experimental streaming-execution agent harness for predictable tool calls. It explores the technical route that predictable side-effect tool calls, such as write, append, mkdir, touch, copy, and controlled edit operations, do not need to interrupt model reasoning on the success path. Informational and high-risk tools remain blocking."
keywords:
  - "LLM agent"
  - "tool calling"
  - "streaming execution"
  - "predictable tool call"
  - "agent harness"
  - "ThinkFlow"
  - "续想"
